      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Honest fair-condition driver that\u2019s a solid option for someone who wants to get in and enjoy the car without paying premium money. It shows some age and use around the body and interior, but it still presents respectably overall and runs and drives as it should. A straightforward, enjoyable car for someone who values a realistic, usable example.",
