      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Exceptionally clean, mint-condition example that presents like a vehicle that has been extremely well cared for. The exterior is outstanding with a deep finish and very minimal signs of wear, the interior is equally impressive with clean, well-kept materials throughout, and it runs and drives exactly as you would hope from a top-condition car. This is not a project or a rough driver\u2014it\u2019s the kind of vehicle a buyer can confidently show, enjoy, and appreciate right away. If you\u2019ve been waiting for a truly standout example, this is one worth seeing.",
