      "description": "$33,900 - Good-condition vehicle that presents well overall and should make a solid, honest buy for someone wanting a clean driver. The exterior and interior show normal wear for the age, but nothing that suggests a rough or neglected example. It appears well-kept overall, with the kind of minor cosmetic imperfections you\u2019d expect on a used car rather than anything excessive. Buyers can expect a respectable, usable vehicle that looks good, feels cared for, and should compare well with other clean, realistically represented cars in this range.",
